(768, 120, 'description', '<span style="color: #4e505f;">One Bedroom Apartments are noticeably larger than studio Apartments and offer the privacy of a separate bedroom from the Lounge.  One Bedroom Apartments are front, side and rear facing and vary in shape and layout with an overall size of 40 – 45 square meters, whilst our very popular Deluxe One Bedroom Apartments are noticeably larger at 54 square meters.  Both types of One Bedroom Apartment have a very well equipped kitchen, with crockery, cutlery, glass and cookware provided.  One bedroom Apartments can fit an extra rollaway bed, when needed, to accommodate a small family but are equally perfect for a couple or single guests. </span>'),
