(2074, 2596, 'description', '<span style="color: #4e505f;">One Bedroom Apartments are noticeably larger than studio Apartments and offer the privacy of a separate bedroom from the Lounge.  One Bedroom Apartments are front, side and rear facing and vary in shape and layout with an overall size of 40 – 45 square meters, whilst our very popular Deluxe One Bedroom Apartments are noticeably larger at 54 square meters.  Both types of One Bedroom Apartment have a very well equipped kitchen, with crockery, cutlery, glass and cookware provided.  One bedroom Apartments can fit an extra rollaway bed, when needed, to accommodate a small family but are equally perfect for a couple or single guests. </span>'),
(2075, 2596, '_description', 'field_5396cb931eebb'),
(2076, 2596, 'specifications', '<p style="color: #4e505f;">An excellent choice for a moderate stay for a single person or couple, all apartments offer:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="color: #4e505f;">\r\n	<li>24 Hour Reception and Concierge</li>\r\n	<li>Air Conditioning</li>\r\n	<li>Airport transfers (charged)</li>\r\n	<li>Breakfast Vouchers (charged)</li>\r\n	<li>Central Heating</li>\r\n	<li>Communal Washing and drying facility</li>\r\n	<li>Daily Housekeeping</li>\r\n	<li>En Suite bathroom</li>\r\n	<li>Flat screen TV</li>\r\n	<li>Hair Dryer</li>\r\n	<li>In Room Safe</li>\r\n	<li>Iron and Ironing Board</li>\r\n	<li>Laundry and Dry Cleaning service (charged)</li>\r\n	<li>Linen and Towels</li>\r\n	<li>Luggage storage</li>\r\n	<li>Regular towel and linen change</li>\r\n	<li>Satellite channels</li>\r\n	<li>Wake Up Service</li>\r\n	<li>Wireless Broadband (Free)</li>\r\n</ul>'),
