(217, 1, '2014-06-20 14:23:40', '2014-06-20 14:23:40', '<p style="color: #4e505f;">Whatever the date, length and purpose of your stay in London, The Harrington serviced residences and apartments have a Special Offer for you, adding even greater value to staying in serviced residences and apartments.  The Harrington serviced residences and apartments are very much larger than central London hotel rooms and offer many more facilities.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Special Offers currently available include:</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;"><strong><a style="color: #000000;" title="The Harrington serviced residences and apartments" href="http://www.theharrington.com/special-offers/advance-purchase-discounts/">Advance Purchase Discount</a></strong>:  get a discounted rate when you pay for your stay on a non-refundable basis at the time of making your reservation.   This also ensures that you pay at the current exchange rate and not what that may be at the time of your stay.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;"><strong><a style="color: #000000;" title="special offers in London serviced residences and apartments" href="http://www.theharrington.com/special-offers/special-offer-discount/">Stay 5 Nights and Save 10%</a></strong>:  benefit from this discount when your stay is for 5 nights or longer without losing out on the flexibility to change dates, or even cancel, if you need to do so.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;"><strong><a style="color: #000000;" title="London Serviced Apartments One Month Stay" href="http://www.theharrington.com/special-offers/london-serviced-apartments-one-month-stay/">One Month Stay</a></strong>: enjoy significantly lower, flat rates when you reserve a stay of one month or longer at our 1 Harrington Gardens serviced apartments.  For a longer stay like this, also consider our newly refurbished apartments of a higher standard and specification at 3 Harrington Gardens.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;"><a style="font-weight: bold; color: #000000;" title="The Harrignton Serviced Residences and Apartments" href="http://www.theharrington.com/special-offers/london-serviced-residences-three-months-stay/">Three Months Stay</a>: even lower, flat rates when you reserve a stay of three months or longer at either 3 Harrington Gardens serviced residence or 1 Harrington Gardens serviced apartments.  On a stay of this length, you really want somewhere that is a home away from home and that is how The Harrington serviced residences and serviced apartments are designed.</p>', 'Special Offer Overview', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'special-offers', '', '', '2014-06-25 08:49:25', '2014-06-25 08:49:25', '', 0, 'http://localhost/v2.theharrington.com/?page_id=217', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(218, 1, '2014-06-20 14:23:40', '2014-06-20 14:23:40', '<h2 style="color: #4e505f;">Special Offers</h2>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Whatever the date, length and purpose of your stay in London, The Harrington serviced residences and apartments have a Special Offer for you, adding even greater value to staying in serviced residences and apartments.  The Harrington serviced residences and apartments are very much larger than central London hotel rooms and offer many more facilities.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Special Offers currently available include:</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;"><strong><a style="color: #000000;" title="The Harrington serviced residences and apartments" href="http://www.theharrington.com/special-offers/advance-purchase-discounts/">Advance Purchase Discount</a></strong>:  get a discounted rate when you pay for your stay on a non-refundable basis at the time of making your reservation.   This also ensures that you pay at the current exchange rate and not what that may be at the time of your stay.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;"><strong><a style="color: #000000;" title="special offers in London serviced residences and apartments" href="http://www.theharrington.com/special-offers/special-offer-discount/">Stay 5 Nights and Save 10%</a></strong>:  benefit from this discount when your stay is for 5 nights or longer without losing out on the flexibility to change dates, or even cancel, if you need to do so.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;"><strong><a style="color: #000000;" title="London Serviced Apartments One Month Stay" href="http://www.theharrington.com/special-offers/london-serviced-apartments-one-month-stay/">One Month Stay</a></strong>: enjoy significantly lower, flat rates when you reserve a stay of one month or longer at our 1 Harrington Gardens serviced apartments.  For a longer stay like this, also consider our newly refurbished apartments of a higher standard and specification at 3 Harrington Gardens.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;"><a style="font-weight: bold; color: #000000;" title="The Harrignton Serviced Residences and Apartments" href="http://www.theharrington.com/special-offers/london-serviced-residences-three-months-stay/">Three Months Stay</a>: even lower, flat rates when you reserve a stay of three months or longer at either 3 Harrington Gardens serviced residence or 1 Harrington Gardens serviced apartments.  On a stay of this length, you really want somewhere that is a home away from home and that is how The Harrington serviced residences and serviced apartments are designed.</p>', 'Special Offers', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '217-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-20 14:23:40', '2014-06-20 14:23:40', '', 217, 'http://localhost/v2.theharrington.com/217-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(219, 1, '2014-06-20 14:24:21', '2014-06-20 14:24:21', '<p style="color: #4e505f;">Take advantage of Advance Purchase discounts providing a lower rate when you book and pay for your stay in full ahead of arrival.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Often, airlines offer advance purchase discounts for Non Refundable tickets, so why not take advantage of the same with your stay ?.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Terms of Advance Purchase Discounts:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="color: #4e505f;">\r\n	<li>Normally 10% Discount from Best Flexible Rate</li>\r\n	<li>Book at least 7 days in advance</li>\r\n	<li>Stay at any time from now up to November 2014</li>\r\n	<li>Full payment within 24 hours of booking.</li>\r\n	<li>Non Refundable.</li>\r\n	<li>We will try to help with any change of dates but a supplement may be payable if rates for the new dates are higher than the original stay.</li>\r\n	<li>Advance Purchase Rates discounts are strictly subject to availability.</li>\r\n	<li>Advance Purchase Rates discount is normally offered up to 7 days prior to arrival.</li>\r\n	<li>We reserve the right to change or remove Advance Purchase Rates Discounts programme at any time without prior notice.  In the event of such a change, existing reservations will be honoured.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Location:</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">The Harrington – 1 Harrington Gardens is handily located 2 minutes’ walk from Gloucester Road tube station, South Kensington, with many shops, supermarkets and restaurants in the immediate vicinity.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Exclusive shopping in London’s Knightsbridge or High Street Kensington is a short tube ride or a 10 minute walk away.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Many of London’s main museums – the Natural History Museum, Science Museum and Victoria &amp; Albert Museum are a short walk from The Harrington.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Now is a great time to take advantage of great Advance Purchase discounts and to secure the serviced apartment of your choice by making your booking <a style="font-weight: bold; color: #000000;" title="advance purchase rates discount at The Harrington serviced apartments" href="http://www.theharrington.com/1-harrington/" target="_blank">securely online on on our web site</a> !</p>', 'Advanced Purchase Discounts', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'advanced-purchase-discounts', '', '', '2014-06-24 10:31:17', '2014-06-24 10:31:17', '', 217, 'http://localhost/v2.theharrington.com/?page_id=219', 0, 'page', '', 0),
