(253, 1, '2014-06-24 10:20:16', '2014-06-24 10:20:16', '<p style="color: #4e505f;">Take advantage of Advance Purchase discounts providing a lower rate when you book and pay for your stay in full ahead of arrival.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Often, airlines offer advance purchase discounts for Non Refundable tickets, so why not take advantage of the same with your stay ?.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Terms of Advance Purchase Discounts:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="color: #4e505f;">\r\n	<li>Normally 10% Discount from Best Flexible Rate</li>\r\n	<li>Book at least 7 days in advance</li>\r\n	<li>Stay at any time from now up to November 2014</li>\r\n	<li>Full payment within 24 hours of booking.</li>\r\n	<li>Non Refundable.</li>\r\n	<li>We will try to help with any change of dates but a supplement may be payable if rates for the new dates are higher than the original stay.</li>\r\n	<li>Advance Purchase Rates discounts are strictly subject to availability.</li>\r\n	<li>Advance Purchase Rates discount is normally offered up to 7 days prior to arrival.</li>\r\n	<li>We reserve the right to change or remove Advance Purchase Rates Discounts programme at any time without prior notice.  In the event of such a change, existing reservations will be honoured.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Location:</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">The Harrington – 1 Harrington Gardens is handily located 2 minutes’ walk from Gloucester Road tube station, South Kensington, with many shops, supermarkets and restaurants in the immediate vicinity.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Exclusive shopping in London’s Knightsbridge or High Street Kensington is a short tube ride or a 10 minute walk away.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Many of London’s main museums – the Natural History Museum, Science Museum and Victoria &amp; Albert Museum are a short walk from The Harrington.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Now is a great time to take advantage of great Advance Purchase discounts and to secure the serviced apartment of your choice by making your booking <a style="font-weight: bold; color: #000000;" title="advance purchase rates discount at The Harrington serviced apartments" href="http://www.theharrington.com/1-harrington/" target="_blank">securely online on on our web site</a> !</p>', 'Advanced Purchase Discounts', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '219-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-24 10:20:16', '2014-06-24 10:20:16', '', 219, 'http://localhost/v2.theharrington.com/219-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
