(265, 1, '2014-06-24 10:32:11', '2014-06-24 10:32:11', '<p style="color: #4e505f;">Enjoy flat weekly rates for your London serviced residences three months stay and more at our 3 Harrington Gardens and 1 Harrington Gardens residences in South Kensington.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Our <a style="font-weight: bold; color: #000000;" title="The Harrington - 3 Harrington Gardens" href="http://www.theharrington.com/properties/3-harrington-gardens/3-harrington-gardens/" target="_blank">3 Harrington Gardens</a> serviced residence features Executive Studio and very Large One Bedroom Apartments newly refurbished throughout with decor and furnishings ideally suited to an extended stay.  Apartments at 3 Harrington Gardens are to a higher specification.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Terms of Special Rates for Three Months and more:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="color: #4e505f;">\r\n	<li>Special Flat Rates for a stay of 3 months and longer.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style="color: #4e505f;">\r\n	<li>Stay at any time from now.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style="color: #4e505f;">\r\n	<li>Credit or debit card details are required to guarantee your reservation.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style="color: #4e505f;">\r\n	<li>Payment of 1 week’s non-refundable deposit one month prior to arrival.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style="color: #4e505f;">\r\n	<li>Payment of balance of the first month on arrival.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style="color: #4e505f;">\r\n	<li>Special rates for London serviced residences three months stay are strictly subject to availability.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style="color: #4e505f;">\r\n	<li>We reserve the right to change or remove Special Offers at any time without prior notice. In the event of such a change, existing reservations will be honoured.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Our London serviced residences three months and longer also include our apartments at <a style="font-weight: bold; color: #000000;" title="The Harrington - 1 Harrington Gardens" href="http://www.theharrington.com/properties/1-harrington-gardens/" target="_blank">1 Harrington Gardens</a>, which are to a lesser specification and budget.  Rates for both serviced residences are <a style="font-weight: bold; color: #000000;" title="London serviced residences three months stay" href="http://www.theharrington.com/availability/" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Location:</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">3 and 1 Harrington Gardens are perfectly located for a longer stay – just 2 minutes’ walk from Gloucester Road tube station, with direct routes to the rest of central London.  There are many shops, supermarkets and restaurants in the immediate vicinity.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Many of London’s main museums are close by. Kensington Gardens and Hyde Park are 10 minutes’ walk and major shopping areas are a short tube ride away.  The Harrington is also close to London’s Earl’s Court and Olympia.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Don’t forget to book your apartment securely at <a style="font-weight: bold; color: #000000;" title="London serviced residences three months stay" href="http://www.theharrington.com/properties/3-harrington-gardens/3-harrington-gardens/" target="_blank">The Harrington web site</a>, on our special rates for London serviced residences three months stay.</p>', 'London Serviced Residences Three Months Stay', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '225-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-24 10:32:11', '2014-06-24 10:32:11', '', 225, 'http://localhost/v2.theharrington.com/225-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
