(267, 1, '2014-06-25 08:32:23', '2014-06-25 08:32:23', '<p style="color: #4e505f;">Whatever the date, length and purpose of your stay in London, The Harrington serviced residences and apartments have a Special Offer for you, adding even greater value to staying in serviced residences and apartments.  The Harrington serviced residences and apartments are very much larger than central London hotel rooms and offer many more facilities.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Special Offers currently available include:</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;"><strong><a style="color: #000000;" title="The Harrington serviced residences and apartments" href="http://www.theharrington.com/special-offers/advance-purchase-discounts/">Advance Purchase Discount</a></strong>:  get a discounted rate when you pay for your stay on a non-refundable basis at the time of making your reservation.   This also ensures that you pay at the current exchange rate and not what that may be at the time of your stay.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;"><strong><a style="color: #000000;" title="special offers in London serviced residences and apartments" href="http://www.theharrington.com/special-offers/special-offer-discount/">Stay 5 Nights and Save 10%</a></strong>:  benefit from this discount when your stay is for 5 nights or longer without losing out on the flexibility to change dates, or even cancel, if you need to do so.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;"><strong><a style="color: #000000;" title="London Serviced Apartments One Month Stay" href="http://www.theharrington.com/special-offers/london-serviced-apartments-one-month-stay/">One Month Stay</a></strong>: enjoy significantly lower, flat rates when you reserve a stay of one month or longer at our 1 Harrington Gardens serviced apartments.  For a longer stay like this, also consider our newly refurbished apartments of a higher standard and specification at 3 Harrington Gardens.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;"><a style="font-weight: bold; color: #000000;